The burden and trend of gastric cancer and possible risk factors in five Asian 
countries from 1990 to 2019.

Ning FL(#)(1), Lyu J(#)(2), Pei JP(#)(3), Gu WJ(4), Zhang NN(5), Cao SY(6), Zeng 
YJ(7), Abe M(8), Nishiyama K(9), Zhang CD(10).

