Cost-effectiveness of multicomponent interventions in type 2 diabetes mellitus 
in a cluster randomised controlled trial: the INDICA study.

García-Pérez L(1)(2)(3), Ramallo-Fariña Y(4)(2)(3), Vallejo-Torres L(4)(2), 
Rodríguez-Rodríguez L(4)(3), González-Pacheco H(4), Santos-Hernández B(4), 
García-Bello MA(4), Wägner AM(5)(6), Carmona M(2)(3)(7), Serrano-Aguilar 
